  "content": "<p data-pid=\"aDBRKoT3\">看起来没有人推荐 Anki 啊，我来介绍一下好了</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"711\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-original-token=\"v2-0300172f7adedaa401bfd1be1a1cca35\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c87f8757826c627c51907ac19ff83dcd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"711\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;711&#39; height=&#39;1920&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"711\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-original-token=\"v2-0300172f7adedaa401bfd1be1a1cca35\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c87f8757826c627c51907ac19ff83dcd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"711\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"5YHbLk8w\">简单来说，用 Anki 可以记录我们平时学到的知识，然后 Anki 会通过算法来安排我们复习，以保证我们能记住 90% 学过的知识。</p><p data-pid=\"tsSqh4Ll\">Anki 是怎么做到的呢？两个关键词：间隔重复、测试效应。</p><p data-pid=\"MC7UlHit\"><b>间隔重复</b>，就是将我们学习过的知识，按照熟悉程度来安排下次复习的日期。Anki 的算法能让大部分知识在我们快要忘掉它们的时候出现在我们面前，提高我们的复习效率，不把时间<b>浪费</b>在复习<b>熟知</b>的知识和<b>重新</b>学习<b>忘记</b>的知识上面。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1207\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-59f792af5a846a1fae48e1777651927f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-934399b249f646388a9e6a82c8b7f473_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1207\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1207&#39; height=&#39;679&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1207\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-59f792af5a846a1fae48e1777651927f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-934399b249f646388a9e6a82c8b7f473_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1207\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"pJnFREdQ\"><b>测试效应</b>，则是通过看问题、想答案的复习方法，激发我们复习的<b>主动性</b>，从而提高我们复习的效果。研究表明，通过这种测试形式的复习，能够提高<b>长期记忆</b>效果 13% ！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1210\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-c38e3b12f8e3135bfc1ed8c27f50934a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f7474fdab0b2c92e83d9fd7f6ed5c71_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1210\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1210&#39; height=&#39;679&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1210\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-c38e3b12f8e3135bfc1ed8c27f50934a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f7474fdab0b2c92e83d9fd7f6ed5c71_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1210\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"yZ51GBT9\">让我们看看 Anki 里是什么样的：</p><p data-pid=\"795fpMpR\">间隔重复：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"366\" data-original-token=\"v2-51c958126ee54810e63de9095b02c4cc\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-14821d24124c852413911a4dbf133dbd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;366&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"366\" data-original-token=\"v2-51c958126ee54810e63de9095b02c4cc\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-14821d24124c852413911a4dbf133dbd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"N3LJxJAO\">测试效应：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-4d53b76867340492916a40df172682a2\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-52112b9a59728b3a2818858cc0064e25_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;634&#39; height=&#39;542&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-4d53b76867340492916a40df172682a2\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-52112b9a59728b3a2818858cc0064e25_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><hr/><p data-pid=\"2qxiG5MH\">Anki 支持windows、mac、linux、安卓、苹果等常见设备，并且可以多端同步，走到哪学到哪。</p><p data-pid=\"qVB_Y00z\">为了帮到有缘人，我写了一份快速上手教程：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61564332\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2e8a109841199b0a18e70ae7bd16ea66_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1220\" data-image-height=\"535\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：B 站 Ankidroid 视频教程与电子书(全平台教程)快速通道</a>",
